member.name: T:Hotcakes.Modules.Core.Api.Rest.AffiliatesHandler
member.summary: This class handles all of the REST API calls for affiliate management

member.name: M:Hotcakes.Modules.Core.Api.Rest.AffiliatesHandler.GetAction(System.String,System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection)
member.summary: The GET method allows the REST API to return one or many affiliate to the application that called it
member.param: Parameters passed in the URL of the REST API call
Name/value pairs from the REST API call querystring. The only expected keys will be byproduct and byslug.
member.returns: String - a JSON representation of the Errors/Content to return. Content will contain the serialized version of AffiliateDTO or list of AffiliateDTO

member.name: M:Hotcakes.Modules.Core.Api.Rest.AffiliatesHandler.PostAction(System.String,System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection,System.String)
member.summary: Allows the REST API to create or update an affiliate
member.param: Parameters passed in the URL of the REST API call. If there is a first parameter found in the URL, the method will assume it is the affiliate ID and that this is an update, otherwise it assumes to create an affiliate.
Name/value pairs from the REST API call querystring. This is not used in this method.
Serialized (JSON) version of the AffiliateDTO object
member.returns: AffiliateDTO - Serialized (JSON) version of the affiliate

member.name: M:Hotcakes.Modules.Core.Api.Rest.AffiliatesHandler.DeleteAction(System.String,System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection,System.String)
member.summary: Allows for the REST API to delete an affiliate from the store
member.param: Parameters passed in the URL of the REST API call. A single parameter (affiliate ID) is expected.
